WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Semua orang wajib melindungi karya asli]

01:06.540 --> 01:10.820
[Wangi Abadi]

01:10.820 --> 01:11.980
[Diadaptasi dari novel "Qianxiangyin" karya Shisilang]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 12]

01:16.720 --> 01:18.450
Seumur hidup, aku paling benci orang yang memanfaatkan relasi,

01:19.110 --> 01:20.580
Istana Wuyue tidak akan menerimamu.

01:20.580 --> 01:21.580
[Istana Wuyue]

01:37.670 --> 01:39.290
Apakah kau begitu ingin masuk ke Istana Wuyue?

01:44.030 --> 01:45.060
