05:18.440 --> 05:19.420
[Lu Li, Sekte Wanxian]
Kenapa bisa begitu lemah?

05:26.470 --> 05:27.300
Aku...

05:27.320 --> 05:28.250
Nona masih muda dan cantik.

05:28.520 --> 05:29.420
Organ tubuh lengkap,

05:29.960 --> 05:31.010
